'''卡倫·雷蒙·保羅·迪雲樸'''（{{lang-en|'''Calum Raymond Paul Davenport'''}}，{{bd|1983年|1月1日|catIdx=Davenport, Calum}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中堅|中堅]]位置，曾效力[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]、[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]及[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]等球會。

==生平==
=== 球會 ===
;高雲地利
迪雲樸在[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]展開[[職業|職業]]球員生涯，效力青年軍時期曾兩奪[[英格蘭足總青年盃|英格蘭足總青年盃]]亞軍。他在[[2000年至2001年英格蘭超級聯賽|2000/01年英超球季]]最後一場比賽肯定降班時首次代表一隊出戰[[布拉德福德城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:布拉德福德城;zh-hk:巴拉福特}-]]<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/1338505.stm |title=高雲地利賽和巴拉福特 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-05-19 |accessdate=2009-02-05}}{{en}}</ref></small>。他要到2002/03年球季才成為球隊主力，更拿下當季高雲地利最佳年青球員<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/coventry_city/3106543.stm |title=迪雲樸對自己有大期望 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-07-29 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2003-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030810050449/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/coventry_city/3106543.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。翌季更拿下高雲地利最佳球員，他為高雲地利上陣84次，入了3球。

;熱刺
迪雲樸在2004年8月以130萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]加盟[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]<small><ref name=spurs>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/3612970.stm |title=熱刺完成迪雲樸轉會 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-08-30 |accessdate=2009-02-05 }}{{en}}</ref></small>，他很快被外借至[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/3635432.stm |title=迪雲樸外借至韋斯咸 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-09-09 |accessdate=2009-02-05}}{{en}}</ref></small>、[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:南安普顿;zh-hk:修咸頓}-]]<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/southampton/4144203.stm |title=迪雲樸暫借至修咸頓 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-01-03 |accessdate=2009-02-05 }}{{en}}</ref></small>及[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/4240222.stm |title=迪雲樸暫借至諾域治 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-09-13 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2021-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211214061628/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/4240222.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

在2006年1月，他回到熱刺，並在主場1-2不敵[[曼聯|曼聯]]的比賽中首次上陣<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/4906576.stm |title=熱刺 1–2 曼聯 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-04-17 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2007-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070106120323/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/4906576.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。他在[[2005年至2006年英格蘭超級聯賽|2005/06年]]季後曾傳出轉會，但在其他後衛受傷後不了了之。迪雲樸在2006年12月作客擊敗2-1[[曼城足球俱乐部|曼城]]的比賽中取得首個熱刺入球<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6164455.stm |title=曼城 1–2 熱刺 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-12-17 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2017-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903213237/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6164455.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。可是，他長期未能在熱刺取得上陣機會，僅為熱刺上陣20次，取得1個入球。

;韋斯咸
迪雲樸在2007年1月18日以300萬英鎊加盟[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]，簽約三年半<small><ref name=whufc>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6274385.stm |title=韋斯咸完成迪雲樸轉會 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-18 |accessdate=2009-02-05 }}{{en}}</ref></small>。他在兩日後第二度為韋斯咸披甲出戰[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]。

在2008年1月18日，他被外借至[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]一個月，並有最終轉會協議<small><ref name="Watford">{{cite web 
 |title=迪雲樸加盟 
 |work=watfordfc.com 
 |url=http://www.watfordfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10400~1219035,00.html 
 |accessdate=2009-02-04 
 |deadurl=yes 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080121082646/http://www.watfordfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10400~1219035%2C00.html 
 |archivedate=2008-01-21 
 }}{{en}}</ref></small>。可是，他不久後在比賽中更隊友碰撞導致頸椎受傷令交易告吹<small><ref>{{cite web |title=屈福特 1 查爾頓 1 |work=watfordfc.com |url=http://www.watfordfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10400~38971,00.html |accessdate=2009-02-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080123114720/http://www.watfordfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0%2C%2C10400~38971%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-01-23 }}{{en}}</ref></small>。他到了[[2008年至2009年英格蘭超級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]才復出，在2008年8月30日對[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]時接應角球，取得首個韋斯咸入球<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7578470.stm |title=韋斯咸 4-1 布力般 |date=2008-08-30 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2008-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080922060018/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7578470.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

在2009年2月1日，他被外借至[[英超|英超]]球會[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]至季尾<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/7866092.stm |title=迪雲樸暫借至新特蘭 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-02-02 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2009-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205101207/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sunderland/7866092.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，獲派上陣8場，於球季結束後返回韋斯咸。

由於官司纏身，韋斯咸會方在2010年3月中與他解約，賠償25萬鎊<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/8573053.stm |title=West Ham terminate contract of defender Calum Davenport |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-03-17 |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003054535/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/8573053.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2010年季前迪雲樸跟隨[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:诺丁汉森林;zh-hk:諾定咸森林}-]]操練<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8886848.stm |title=Calum Davenport in training with Nottingham Forest |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-05 |accessdate=2010-08-05 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809015122/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8886848.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，其後加盟非聯賽球隊[[Wootton_Blue_Cross_F.C.|禾頓藍十字]]（Wootton Blue Cross）爭取上陣機會以恢復比賽狀態，據稱[[列斯聯足球會|-{zh-hans:利兹联; zh-hk:列斯聯;}-]]一直跟進其進展<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6365422,00.html |title=Leeds to track Davenport |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-09-08 |accessdate=2010-09-09 |archive-date=2010-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101011155707/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6365422,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 國家隊 ===
迪雲樸曾為英格蘭U-17及U-19代表隊上陣，於2003年10月5日首次獲召加入[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|21歲以下足球代表隊]]<small><ref>{{cite news  |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/U21s/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2003/10/68849.htm  |title=Youth breathe life into U21s  |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足球總會]]官網  |date=2003-10-05  |accessdate=2009-02-05  |archive-date=2018-09-29  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929021237/http://www.thefa.com/England/U21s/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2003/10/68849.htm  |dead-url=no  }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

==遇刺事件==
2009年8月21日深夜迪雲樸與母親在位於金斯頓（Kempston）的居所門前遭人持刀刺傷，迪雲樸雙腿被刺，需要接受緊急[[手術|手術]]治療，事後兩人被捕<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/8216100.stm |title=Two held over footballer stabbing |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2009-08-22 |accessdate=2009-08-23 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109031947/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/8216100.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，據報迪雲樸手術後情況仍然嚴重但穩定<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/8216650.stm |title=Police probe footballer stabbing |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2009-08-23 |accessdate=2009-08-23 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003060601/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/8216650.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。10月28日迪雲樸仍然留院，但遭控訴襲擊其姊卡拉（Cara Davenport），獲准保釋待11月10日上庭，卡拉的男友則被控傷害迪雲樸及其母親，迪雲樸透過公關公司發表聲明否認有做錯及不會認罪<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/8330403.stm |title=Player on sister assault charge |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2009-10-28 |accessdate=2009-10-29 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126040511/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/8330403.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。11月10日迪雲樸出庭應訊，被控襲擊其姊卡拉並造成身體傷害，他否認控罪，獲准保釋候審，案件將會轉介[[皇室法庭|皇室法庭]]（Crown Court）於2010年1月12日再開庭<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/beds/bucks/herts/8352323.stm |title=Player denies assault on sister |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2009-11-10 |accessdate=2009-11-11 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003054852/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/beds/bucks/herts/8352323.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。迪雲樸在庭上否認控罪，獲准保釋，押後到8月2日再審<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/northamptonshire/8478662.stm |title=West Ham player Calum Davenport denies sister assault |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2010-01-25 |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128210917/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/northamptonshire/8478662.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。據案情透露，當晚喝酒半醉的迪雲樸與父親一同到姊姊卡拉的居所，其時卡拉與4歲兒子小卡倫（Calum Junior）在睡覺，小卡倫的父親正在坐監，而卡拉剛懷有新男友的骨肉，迪雲樸父子兩人吵醒卡拉，並不斷出言辱罵她，迪雲樸稱卡拉為「婊子」後，在門廊以頭撞其姊，在掙扎間更意外擊中其面頰，卡拉逃脫並即時聯絡男友沃雷爾·韋特靴斯（Worrell Whitehurst），後者隨即趕到迪雲樸家中並發生刺人事件<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10439100 |title=Former West Ham star Calum Davenport 'butted' sister |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2010-06-29 |accessdate=2010-08-05 |archive-date=2018-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121103128/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10439100 |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。迪雲樸辯稱當日三人為卡拉如何養育其腹中骨肉發生激辯，卡拉試圖驅逐父親離開，迪雲樸阻止而發生推撞。據報迪雲樸經常支付小卡倫的衣服及假期費用，並協助姊姊交房租<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10450837 |title=Attack accused footballer was 'defending father' |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2010-06-29 |accessdate=2010-08-05 |archive-date=2018-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121103138/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10450837 |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2010年7月1日迪雲樸獲判無罪<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10473008 |title=Footballer Calum Davenport cleared of sister attack |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2010-07-01 |accessdate=2010-08-05 |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021061028/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10473008 |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而韋特靴斯則因嚴重傷害他人身體罪成被判入獄6年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10605156 |title=Man jailed for stabbing footballer Calum Davenport |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News |date=2010-07-12 |accessdate=2010-08-05 |archive-date=2018-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181122082435/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/10605156 |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

